data.title: ZOHS Automotive Insurance
data.content: Developed a machine learning-based recommendation system using advanced algorithms, including a stacking model, for recommending insurance types. The project integrated real-time streaming, scheduled model retraining, and deployment pipelines using Kafka, Airflow, Kubeflow, and Azure Cloud.

data.title: Yema7D
data.content: Yema7D is a web platform developed to generate didactic mini-scenarios for educational games. It utilizes recurrent autoregressive models to create context-specific scenarios based on provided educational mechanics. The platform is designed to help educators and game developers craft engaging, educational gameplay experiences
